|\lambda^T b | \leq \|\lambda\| \|b\| = \|\lambda\| \leq 1
\sum_i b_i^2 = 1
|b_i| \leq 1
\sum_i \lambda_i b_i \leq \sum_i \lambda_i |b_i| \leq \sum_i \lambda_i =1
\sqrt{n} \sum_i \lambda_i b_i \leq \sqrt{n}
B=\sqrt{n}
